➜戴上科学滤镜后，竟然发现无惨可能是颗大肿瘤？《鬼灭之刃》的医学解读
https://pansci.asia/archives/202524	7200
<ul><li>文／安之｜既来之则安之，目前在念兽医系。</li></ul>
<p>近期最火红的日本动漫《鬼灭之刃》，讲述了在大正时代，猎鬼人与鬼搏斗的故事。</p>
<p>身为王道漫画，对主角而言不可或缺的是目标，好比火影忍者的鸣人渴盼成为火影、航海王的鲁夫渴望成为海贼王一样，《鬼灭之刃》的主人公竈门炭治郎，在几乎全家被鬼惨遭杀害后，给了他要杀了这一切的始作俑者——<strong>鬼舞辻无惨</strong>的强烈动机。</p>
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="451" height="628" src="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/MV5BZjZjNzI5MDctY2Y4YS00NmM4LTljMmItZTFkOTExNGI3ODRhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjc3MjQzNTI@._V1_-451x628.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-202525" srcset="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/MV5BZjZjNzI5MDctY2Y4YS00NmM4LTljMmItZTFkOTExNGI3ODRhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjc3MjQzNTI@._V1_-451x628.jpg 451w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/MV5BZjZjNzI5MDctY2Y4YS00NmM4LTljMmItZTFkOTExNGI3ODRhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjc3MjQzNTI@._V1_-366x510.jpg 366w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/MV5BZjZjNzI5MDctY2Y4YS00NmM4LTljMmItZTFkOTExNGI3ODRhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjc3MjQzNTI@._V1_-103x143.jpg 103w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/MV5BZjZjNzI5MDctY2Y4YS00NmM4LTljMmItZTFkOTExNGI3ODRhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjc3MjQzNTI@._V1_.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 451px) 100vw, 451px" /><figcaption>在《鬼灭之刃》中，主角与鬼杀队一同踏上了消灭鬼、鬼王无惨的征途。图／<a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt9335498/mediaviewer/rm1955564033/">IMDb</a></figcaption></figure></div>
